 false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 18, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "May Day, formally known as International Workers' Day,\u00a0stands\u00a0as a quintessential emblem of extreme leftist ideology.", "large_image": "xH8wXLu46juwbWzK.png", "title": "May Day Demonstrated How High America's Stakes are for the Midterms"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsPiZoIB", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 715, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8610467, "raw_content": "", "author": "truthtoday2022", "created": 1778429429610, "profile_picture": "iYGqi7B2EcZh", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "wst4", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPiZoIB.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/aD1UHib4z2wZ.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/az9nnAQc6VRmt0C9.png", "width": 655, "content-type": "png", "height": 458}], "blurhash": "U1QmCr0000ITXl0JD$H?00^+xaf*%g0000Ri", "full_resolution": [458, 655]}, "title": "Pronouns = retard identifier", "last_comment_created": 1778506457854, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 22, "score_up": 715, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2053519228737880517", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsPjh6Tw", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 240, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8611040, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1778450626042, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "lash", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPjh6Tw.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/hitchslap1/status/2053519228737880517", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Higher IQ Means Less Violent", "last_comment_created": 1778472642165, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 11, "score_up": 240, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 1200, "heightRatio": 72, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGQyEy0a4AA0f0S.png", "height": 864}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1776873601000, "id": "2046982365684052242", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1225912347849420800/39fqZKGW_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Steve Stewart-Williams", "username": "SteveStuWill"}, "content": "Smarter People Are Less Violent\n\n\"The prevalence of violent behavior dropped steadily with increasing IQ: 16.3% of individuals with IQs in the 70-79 range reported violent behavior, compared with just 2.9% of those with IQs of 120-129.\"\n\nhttps://t.co/4XMLOE0add", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1776}, "images": [{"width": 750, "heightRatio": 70, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HH-Q2nfacAAGInm.jpg", "height": 526}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 89, "created": 1778432111000, "id": "2053519228737880517", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1867206799121895424/YpyOkoot_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Hitchslap", "username": "Hitchslap1"}, "content": "High IQ people are less violent. IQ matters for nearly everything that society cares about.\n\nI wish more people understood this.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2347}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsPjj1h3", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 20, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8611729, "raw_content": "\u201cI am with you alway.\u201d\nMatthew 28:20\n\nIt is well there is One who is ever the same, and who is ever with us. It is well there is one stable rock amidst the billows of the sea of life. O my soul, set not thine affections upon rusting, moth-eaten, decaying treasures, but set thine heart upon him who abides forever faithful to thee. Build not thine house upon the moving quicksands of a deceitful world, but found thy hopes upon this rock, which, amid descending rain and roaring floods, shall stand immovably secure. \n\nMy soul, I charge thee, lay up thy treasure in the only secure cabinet; store thy jewels where thou canst never lose them. Put thine all in Christ; set all thine affections on his person, all thy hope in his merit, all thy trust in his efficacious blood, all thy joy in his presence, and so thou mayest laugh at loss, and defy destruction. \n\nRemember that all the flowers in the world\u2019s garden fade by turns, and the day cometh when nothing will be left but the black, cold earth. Death\u2019s black extinguisher must soon put out thy candle. Oh! how sweet to have sunlight when the candle is gone! The dark flood must soon roll between thee and all thou hast; then wed thine heart to him who will never leave thee; trust thyself with him who will go with thee through the black and surging current of death\u2019s stream, and who will land thee safely on the celestial shore, and make thee sit with him in heavenly places forever. \n\nGo, sorrowing son of affliction, tell thy secrets to the Friend who sticketh closer than a brother. Trust all thy concerns with him who never can be taken from thee, who will never leave thee, and who will never let thee leave him, even \u201cJesus Christ, the same yesterday, and today, and forever.\u201d \n\n\u201cLo, I am with you alway,\u201d is enough for my soul to live upon, let who will forsake me.", "author": "AslanFan", "created": 1778499196461, "profile_picture": "PkOG3emTH2Im", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Morning, May 11 - Morning & Evening, C. H. Spurgeon", "last_comment_created": 1778499196460, "content": "<p>\u201cI am with you alway.\u201d\nMatthew 28:20</p>\n<p>It is well there is One who is ever the same, and who is ever with us. It is well there is one stable rock amidst the billows of the sea of life. O my soul, set not thine affections upon rusting, moth-eaten, decaying treasures, but set thine heart upon him who abides forever faithful to thee. Build not thine house upon the moving quicksands of a deceitful world, but found thy hopes upon this rock, which, amid descending rain and roaring floods, shall stand immovably secure.</p>\n<p>My soul, I charge thee, lay up thy treasure in the only secure cabinet; store thy jewels where thou canst never lose them. Put thine all in Christ; set all thine affections on his person, all thy hope in his merit, all thy trust in his efficacious blood, all thy joy in his presence, and so thou mayest laugh at loss, and defy destruction.</p>\n<p>Remember that all the flowers in the world\u2019s garden fade by turns, and the day cometh when nothing will be left but the black, cold earth. Death\u2019s black extinguisher must soon put out thy candle. Oh! how sweet to have sunlight when the candle is gone! The dark flood must soon roll between thee and all thou hast; then wed thine heart to him who will never leave thee; trust thyself with him who will go with thee through the black and surging current of death\u2019s stream, and who will land thee safely on the celestial shore, and make thee sit with him in heavenly places forever.</p>\n<p>Go, sorrowing son of affliction, tell thy secrets to the Friend who sticketh closer than a brother. Trust all thy concerns with him who never can be taken from thee, who will never leave thee, and who will never let thee leave him, even \u201cJesus Christ, the same yesterday, and today, and forever.\u201d</p>\n<p>\u201cLo, I am with you alway,\u201d is enough for my soul to live upon, let who will forsake me.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 20, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsPjh6cE", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 222, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8611062, "raw_content": "", "author": "kek_saved_the_world", "created": 1778451956909, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Easzq8", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPjh6cE.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/k0TaNgXPaoGR.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_